text: "Questions 67 and 68" is a 1969 debut single by Chicago. It was taken from their debut studio album Chicago Transit Authority. It went to number 71 in the United States, number 79 in France, number 54 in Canada and went to number 24 in the United States when it was re-released in 1971. ==References== Category:1969 songs Category:Debut singles Category:Jazz fusion Category:Chicago (band) songs
title: Questions 67 and 68
